flowchart TD
  Start([Trader / user]) --> Land[Lands on the marketplace website]
  Land --> Browse[Browse community & KOL listings]
  Browse --> Pick[Select a community]
  Pick --> Tier{Access type?}

  Tier -->|Public / discovery| Public[Public join info or link]
  Public --> Group1([Enter Telegram group])

  Tier -->|VIP / paid / private| Pay[Complete payment]
  Pay --> Confirm{Payment OK?}
  Confirm -->|No| Pay
  Confirm -->|Yes| Link[Receive invite / access link]
  Link --> Group2([Enter Telegram group])

  Group1 --> Use[Use discussion & signals for trading]
  Group2 --> Use
